				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ph%E1%BB%93n/Lu%E1%BA%ADn-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-gNyuXuF7yPPhB-huS3ehnQ">Luận thi kỳ 1 - 論詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Ph%E1%BB%93n/author-5gmuZmguwm6161F8wvDGRQ">Triệu Phồn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Chi-T%C3%A0i/Nam-Vi%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0nh/poem-UDjY9jOq9_mlyDx0KGyaRQ">Nam Việt hành - 南越行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Chi-T%C3%A0i/author-9i8XaM0gzFC7E9e0G52Oug">Chu Chi Tài</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Nguy%E1%BB%87t-xu%E1%BA%A5t-3/poem-togWbJ5UmSRGYROQ4O2o9A">Nguyệt xuất 3 - 月出 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%B1-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-lai-ng%C3%B4n-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-s%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-CFGlXtKzg-7M-QcXEABMCw">Nhân tự Bắc Ninh lai, ngôn Bắc Ninh sự cảm tác - 人自北寧來言北寧事感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-c%E1%BB%95-ca/poem-SQLcZneUoty6Zn7UCfgM4Q">Thạch cổ ca - 石鼓歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/Thu-t%E1%BB%A9-t%E1%BA%B7ng-vi%E1%BB%85n/poem-4iXezOkLOappwMuTJCE7RQ">Thu tứ tặng viễn - 秋思贈遠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/author-RmmfVoamdwhG77VOgdRDUQ">Trương Trọng Tố</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%C3%A0-S%C6%A1n-h%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%A1c/poem-HBv288KED1uuwEA4s011sA">Trà Sơn hạ tác - 茶山下作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/U-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A2n-tu%E1%BA%BF-t%C3%A1c/poem-iYpPD6KWd8X-T-XaF9hWhw">U Châu tân tuế tác - 幽州新歲作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy%E1%BB%87t/author-AKTNQoEgmd-YADK1_8RKQg">Trương Duyệt</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
